Class HJBSessionItems

java.lang.Object
  hjb.jms.HJBSessionItems
Direct Known Subclasses:
HJBSessionConsumers, HJBSessionDurableSubscribers, HJBSessionProducers, HJBSessionQueueBrowsers
public abstract class HJBSessionItems
extends Object

HJBSessionItems is a base class that provides behaviour common to those classes that represent items created using the Session created by a HJBConnection.

Author:
Tim Emiola
